      "code": "# Build a list of candidate hadiths with approximate similarity to the full span\ndef search_hadith_candidates(query, topn=20):\n    scores=[]\n    for i, h in enumerate(hadith):\n        text = h.get('Matn') or h.get('hadithTxt') or ''\n        if not text:\n            continue\n        # quick filter: look for any key term present in normalized?\n        norm_text = normalize_ar(text)\n        # if neither \"يبتلي\" nor \"الْمُنافِقين/المنافق\" present, skip maybe\n        # but we can compute ratio anyway; but there are 35k entries, computing ratio for all is fine.\n        ratio = sim_ratio(query, text)\n        if ratio>0.2: # keep coarse threshold\n            scores.append((ratio, token_f1(query, text), i, text))\n    scores.sort(key=lambda x:(x[0],x[1]), reverse=True)\n    return scores[:topn]\n\ncands = search_hadith_candidates(span_full, topn=30)\nlen(cands), cands[:5][0][0] if cands else None",
